  "Upward as temperature increases on the graph": "",
  "Perfectly flat across all temperature ranges shown": "",
  "Randomly with no clear pattern or direction shown": "",
  "Downward showing solubility decreases with temperature": "",
  "Gas solubility curves slope downward because gas solubility decreases as temperature increases. Warm liquids hold less dissolved gas.": "",
