  "An unsaturated solution because 25 g is less than the 30 g maximum": "",
  "A supersaturated solution because she dissolved a large amount": "",
  "A suspension because the KNO3 will settle out of the water": "",
  "Since 25 g is less than the maximum solubility of 30 g/100 mL at 20 degrees C, the solution is unsaturated. She could dissolve 5 more grams before reaching saturation.": "",
  "A student reads that NaCl has a solubility of 36 g/100 mL at 20 degrees C and 39 g/100 mL at 100 degrees C. What can the student conclude?": "",
