  "160 grams of KNO3 crystallizes from the cooled solution": "",
  "170 grams of KNO3 crystallizes from the cooled solution": "",
  "At 20 degrees C, only 30 g can stay dissolved. She started with 160 g dissolved, so 160 - 30 = 130 g crystallizes out when cooled.": "",
